content: You'll awaken in this new realm hiding inside an offering chest for a mysterious "Lady", being carried to The Webbed Hollow by two Yaoguai. Eventually, your fiend Zhu Bajie will grow tired of hiding, but before you can bust out, a mysterious woman will eliminate the two Wushan Lesser Guai.
